## ERROR HANDLING
- If Google Places returns no results, exit gracefully with message
- If a website times out, continue to next shop, log the failure
- If Claude API fails on a shop, set all review signals to null and continue
- Rate limit Google Places calls: 100ms delay between requests
- Rate limit Claude API calls: 500ms delay between requests
- If script crashes mid-run, log last completed shop so you know where to restart

## PACKAGE.JSON SCRIPTS
- "start": runs the CLI
- "scout": alias for start  
- "test:places": tests Google Places connection with a single known shop
- "test:scraper": tests scraper on a single URL passed as argument
- "test:claude": tests Claude API connection with dummy review text

